1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Bb4+ 4. Bd2 Qe7 5. g3 Nc6 6. Nc3 O-O (6... d5 {
is not a very successful mix of Bogo-Indian and Ragozin defense.} 7. a3 Bxc3 8.
Bxc3 Ne4 (8... O-O 9. Bg2 $14) 9. Qc2 O-O 10. Bg2 {with a small, but stable
advantage as in the game 1-0 (90) Dragun, K (2530)-Warakomski, T (2489)
Koszalin 2014}) 7. Bg2 d6 {In this chapter Black tries to keep his
dark-squared bishop away from the exchange, at least for a while.} (7... Na5 {
This unexpected move shall also be mentioned. White should meet it by} 8. c5 $1
{grabbing more space and forcing Black to part with his dark-squared bishop.} (
{Black gets a decent position after modest} 8. b3 b6 9. O-O Bb7 10. Qc2 Rfc8 {
followed by d7-d5 or c7-c5, according to circumstances. I had a game in this
line: ½-½ (81) Postny,E (2651)-Bauer,C (2672) Belfort 2012}) 8... Nc6 (8...
Nc4 9. Bg5 h6 10. Bxf6 Bxc3+ 11. bxc3 Qxf6 12. Qa4 d5 13. cxd6 Nxd6 14. O-O $14
{1-0 (64) Sanikidze, T (2586)-Khukhashvili, S (2396) Baku 2012}) (8... b6 9. a3
Bxc3 10. Bxc3 $14) 9. a3 Bxc3 10. Bxc3 Ne4 (10... d5 11. b4 $14 {1-0 (35)
Pelletier,Y (2566)-Ovsejevitsch,S (2588) Switzerland 2016}) 11. Qd3 Nxc3 12.
Qxc3 d5 (12... d6 13. Rc1 Bd7 14. O-O $14 {1-0 (64) Goganov,A (2592)-Slavin,A 
(2367) Sochi 2017}) 13. b4 a6 14. O-O $14 {1-0 (32) Ni,H (2681)-Wang,C (2514)
China 2016}) 8. d5 Ne5 (8... exd5 9. Nxd5 Bxd2+ 10. Qxd2 Qd8 11. O-O {leads to
a typical position, where White enjoys the space advantage.}) 9. Nxe5 dxe5 10.
a3 Bc5 11. O-O exd5 12. cxd5 {The d5 pawn is well protected and yields White
some space advantage.} h6 13. Rc1 a6 14. Qc2 {Jakovenko, definitely, came well
prepared for this game, as Amin has already played this line before.} (14. Qb3
Bd6 15. Rfd1 Bd7 16. h3 Rfb8 17. e4 b5 18. Ne2 a5 $11 {1/2-1/2 (41) Wang,Y 
(2718)-Amin, B (2627) Tromsoe 2014}) 14... Bd6 15. Nd1 $1 {Good maneuver. The
knight is going to e3, where it has better prospects.} e4 16. Ne3 Re8 17. Bc3 {
After a fine regrouping White achieved a slight advantage in the game 1-0 (79)
Jakovenko, D (2748)-Amin, B (2636) Baku 2015} *

